'''資訊、通訊及媒體發展管理局'''（{{lang-en|Infocomm Media Development Authority, '''IMDA'''}}）是[[新加坡政府|新加坡政府]][[新加坡政府法定机构|法定机构]]，隶属于[[新加坡通讯及新闻部|通讯及新闻部]]（MCI）。

== 历史 ==
2016年8月16日，议会通过《信息传播媒体发展管理局法案》之后，IMDA于当年9月30日正式成立。此前，信息通信发展管理局（IDA）和[[媒体发展管理局|媒体发展管理局]]（MDA）进行改组并合并。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Parliament passes Info-communications Media Development Authority Bill - Channel NewsAsia|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/parliament-passes-info/3048966.html|accessdate=2019-11-01|date=2016-08-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826220615/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/parliament-passes-info/3048966.html|archivedate=2016-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=IMDA to Empower Businesses, Workers and Communities to Seize Opportunities in a Digital Future|url=http://www.imda.gov.sg/news-and-events/Media-Room/Media-Releases/2016/imda-to-empower-businesses-workers-and-communities-to-seize-opportunities-in-a-digital-future|accessdate=2019-11-01|work=Infocomm Media Development Authority|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101095554/https://www2.imda.gov.sg/news-and-events/Media-Room/Media-Releases/2016/imda-to-empower-businesses-workers-and-communities-to-seize-opportunities-in-a-digital-future|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 关键功能 ==
IMDA提供各种对行业，社区的计划，政策和捐款。 IMDA另通过个人数据保护委员会（PDPC）保护用户隐私。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=IDA, MDA restructuring to create new entities (Amended)|url=https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/technology/ida-mda-restructuring-to-create-new-entities-amended|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=Choudhury|date=2016-01-19|first=Amit Roy|work=The Business Times|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101095712/https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/technology/ida-mda-restructuring-to-create-new-entities-amended|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=About IMDA|url=http://www.imda.gov.sg/Who-We-Are/about-imda|accessdate=2019-11-01|work=Infocomm Media Development Authority|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505232229/https://www.imda.gov.sg/Who-We-Are/about-imda|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 关键举措 ==

* '''中小企业数字化''' - 以一种计划为企业提供已批准的数字化方案，并协助他们将业务进行数字化。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Singapore Budget 2019: SMEs Go Digital programme to be expanded|url=https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/government-economy/singapore-budget-2019/singapore-budget-2019-smes-go-digital-programme-to-be|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=Lee|date=2019-02-18|first=Jamie|work=The Business Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028150536/https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/government-economy/singapore-budget-2019/singapore-budget-2019-smes-go-digital-programme-to-be|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=SMEs Go Digital|url=http://www.imda.gov.sg/programme-listing/smes-go-digital|accessdate=2019-11-01|work=Infocomm Media Development Authority|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501050808/https://www.imda.gov.sg/programme-listing/smes-go-digital|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''数字经济行动框架''' - 其目的在通过加快工业和企业的数字化进程，提高国际竞争力以及通过前沿技术改造信息通信和媒体部门，从而增强新加坡的数字优势。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Singapore’s IMDA introduces Digital Economy Framework for Action to promote collaboration|url=https://www.opengovasia.com/singapores-imda-introduces-digital-economy-framework-for-action-to-promote-collaboration/|accessdate=2019-11-01|date=2018-05-22|work=OpenGov Asia|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101101044/https://www.opengovasia.com/singapores-imda-introduces-digital-economy-framework-for-action-to-promote-collaboration/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''服务4.0''' - 提供计划以帮助企业满足新兴技术推动的新服务行业的计划。 有些是针对中小ICE企业的GOCLOUD，Pixel和数字服务实验室（DSL）的方案<ref>{{Cite web|title=In pursuit of Services 4.0 - a Singapore perspective|url=https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/opinion/in-pursuit-of-services-40-a-singapore-perspective|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=Bose|date=2019-02-26|first=Mohit Mehrotra, Samrat|work=The Business Times|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101095547/https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/opinion/in-pursuit-of-services-40-a-singapore-perspective|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=IMDA identifies Services 4.0 as future of services in a digital economy|url=https://www.connectedtoindia.com/imda-identifies-services-40-as-future-of-services-in-a-digital-economy-4820.html|accessdate=2019-11-01|work=www.connectedtoindia.com|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125140244/https://www.connectedtoindia.com/imda-identifies-services-40-as-future-of-services-in-a-digital-economy-4820.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Singapore Technology Roadmap identifies Services 4.0 as the future of services|url=https://www.digitalnewsasia.com/digital-economy/singapore-technology-roadmap-identifies-services-40-future-services|accessdate=2019-11-01|date=2018-11-23|work=Digital News Asia|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120140615/https://www.digitalnewsasia.com/digital-economy/singapore-technology-roadmap-identifies-services-40-future-services|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''数字准备''' - 一项提供计划的计划，旨在帮助新加坡人积极，负责任和自信地使用技术。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Digital Readiness|url=http://www.imda.gov.sg/for-community/digital-readiness|accessdate=2019-11-01|work=Infocomm Media Development Authority|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417220927/https://www.imda.gov.sg/for-community/digital-readiness|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* '''技术加速器（TeSA）''' - 与新加坡技能机构的一项合作计划，旨在为[[数字经济|数字经济]]做好准备。它为技术人员建立和发展ICT技能提供计划和赠款。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=TechSkills Accelerator (TeSA)|url=http://www.imda.gov.sg/programme-listing/TechSkills-Accelerator-TeSA|accessdate=2019-12-09|work=Infocomm Media Development Authority|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501053830/https://www.imda.gov.sg/programme-listing/TechSkills-Accelerator-TeSA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

